item.description: Ana Nora (Sovarel) Evans University of Virginia AnaNEvans@virginia.edu Research &nbsp · &nbsp Teaching &nbsp · &nbsp Other Activities &nbsp · &nbsp Personal I am a PhD candidate at the University of Virginia, advised by Professors Mary Lou Soffa and Sebastian Elbaum. I am working on oracles for autonomous vehicles. I have a MS in Mathematics (2014) and Master of Computer Science (2006), both from UVA.
